msgstr "快適な滞在のための設備がそろった、モダンなお部屋をご用意しています。"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.homepage
msgid "Next"
msgstr "次へ"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that they relax, you can offer extra services to make your guests fill "
"even more\n"
"            comfortable!"
msgstr ""
"ゲストがさらに快適に過ごせるよう、追加サービスを\n"
"            提供しましょう!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that you have several companies or branches, you may want some of your "
"employees to access only to some of them in case they always work in some of "
"your places."
msgstr ""
"複数の会社や支社を管理している場合、特定の従業員が常に特定の拠点で勤務するよ"
