#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odooは無限の可能性を提供します:"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
